Beatriz Ferreyra

              —
              Huellas Entreveradas
            
              (Persistence of Sound)
label: Persistence of Sound
description:
Original GRM member Beatriz Ferreyra deploys a gripping trio of concrète works spanning 40 years (1977-2007) and revealing some of her most mysterious, freeform and otherworldly work comparable to Schaeffer and Parmegiani, but with a poetic playfulness of her own.
